snippet.textDisplay:
For anyone wondering what happened to Wendy- during a pre recording at sbs she was told to go on a platform, but it wasn’t raised and she fell 3.5 meters injuring her wrist, pelvis, and face.
Because of this there will most likely be no promotions and she will be out for up to 6 months. This is also not the first time idols have had problems with sbs stages, and despite all that all they did was give a weak apology.

Best wishes to Wendy and red velvet💕
